--input-shadow-hover-light.light: 0px 4px 8px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16), inset 0px -1px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04), inset 0px 0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), inset 0px 2px 0.75px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), inset 0px -3px 0.75px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)

--input-shadow-light.light: 0px 4px 8px -4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16), inset 0px -1px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04), inset 0px 0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), inset 0px 2px 0.75px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), inset 0px -3px 0.75px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04)

--toggle-thumb-enabled-shadow-light.light: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), inset 0px -1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), inset 0px -4px 4px hsla(var(--interactive-accent-hsl), 0.15)

--toggle-thumb-shadow-light.light: 0px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), inset 0px -1px 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4), inset 0px -4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)

--color-accent-3-light.light: hsla( var(--accent-h), calc(0.4 * var(--accent-s)), calc(0.81 * var(--accent-l)) )

box-shadow.dark: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--background-modifier-active-hover), inset 0 2px 4px 0 var(--background-modifier-active-hover), inset 0 1px 1px 1px var(--background-modifier-active-hover)

filter.dark: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
